Synopsis:
Shadowheart finally meets Nightsong. If Shadowheart is an Avatar, the player has the option to kill or free Nightsong. Shar will encourage the player to kill Nightsong using the Spear of Night.

If the player is controlling a companion Shadowheart, Shadowheart will always choose to kill Nightsong.
